files.description: The sole EHI export documentation: a 4-page PDF with basic step-by-step instructions for performing single-patient and bulk population EHI exports from Axiom. Contains screenshots of the export interface but no data dictionary, format specification, or schema. Created 2026-01-30 by Khalid Maskari.
